informations.information:
This world has 4 popular or noteworthy religions.

Yuklin (Demon Sect)

  • Domains: Death, Air, and Void
  • Holy Symbol: Skull and Crossbones
  • From the Yuxue culture.

Drokki (Mystical)

  • Domains: Glory, Protection, and Nobility
  • Holy Symbol: Lance
  • From the Belegola culture.

Levervy (Monotheistic)

  • Domains: Chaos, Death, and Law
  • Holy Symbol: Flame
  • From the Oglesereux culture.

Kingsridge (Mystical)

  • Domains: Nobility, Magic, and Liberation
  • Holy Symbol: Crown
  • From the Fleodie culture.
